Ukraine’s Grain Harvest Will Be 54.5 Million Tons, Group Says

-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 
2011-12-01T14:03:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-01/ukraine-s-grain-harvest-will-be-54-5-million-tons-group-says.html
Ukraine’s grain harvest in net
weight will be a record 54.5 million tons this year, exceeding
the previous all-time high of 53.2 million tons in 2008,
according to the country’s Agrarian Confederation.  The grain harvest in bunker weight will be 57.8 million
tons this year, Sergey Stoianov, director of the producers’
group, said in a statement on the confederation’s  website  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  